{"tid":849572,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"美國回流問前景 BI/ BA","createTime":"2018-10-05T18:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-12T06:48:21.000Z","uid":37309,"like":0,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"01fa0c5148f516413e3217ebfbc9ad0f53b6ad2e","tid":849572,"uid":37309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T18:40:43.000Z","msg":"小弟中五0分過左美國讀書， 讀完dual majors in marketing, and management information system.跟手就係local讀埋一個master in business intelligence &amp; analytics. 本身記唔想好似讀完書就番去咁柒。所以美國搵工， 好好彩搵到間fortune 50既公司番 番緊financial associate 既職位。 小弟想問下香港呢行前景如何， 有咩skill set 可以再加分？小弟背景有six sigma green belt, google analytics certification, 準備想考番個CAPM( certified associates in project management)  有sql, python, r ,jmp, sas 呢類型數據software 既experience. <br />\n<br />\n我plan緊下年年尾， 草夠啲經驗就番香港， 美國做野實在太悶，人事都唔算太好。 唔知各位師兄有冇咩經驗指教下 等我再準備多啲先番香港？ <br />\nBusiness analyst 前程如何？ 如果差又有咩其他關於data 既title好做啲？"},{"pid":"4dfabde44f77541f622da026c861f9bce642182f","tid":849572,"uid":203889,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔好返黎<br />\n認真，人事閪邊度都有，港資老細仲閪<br />\n你諗係果邊轉工好過"},{"pid":"50f84f4d29e76781f7997cc42e2444a1dc24313b","tid":849572,"uid":17111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T19:56:05.000Z","msg":"你做緊既financial associate 工作內容係做咩？"},{"pid":"cfc6ae958a7fb7efd76e5bbdfec4fd12ccd76f1c","tid":849572,"uid":37309,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"4dfabde44f77541f622da026c861f9bce642182f","tid":849572,"uid":203889,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T19:30:58.000Z","msg":"唔好返黎<br />\n認真，人事閪邊度都有，港資老細仲閪<br />\n你諗係果邊轉工好過"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T12:48:34.000Z","msg":"人好好 但係工作環境太悶 生活都好悶..."},{"pid":"36b16d30305fd9758573f02e977d32b928fb4d42","tid":849572,"uid":37309,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"50f84f4d29e76781f7997cc42e2444a1dc24313b","tid":849572,"uid":17111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018